            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Colocar uma string entre os colchetes cria um array com um valor, experimente com <code>\"Tom\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" friends = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Tom&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"];\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(friends);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"17\" endIndex=\"22\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"[ 'Tom' ]\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>\"Tom\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
