            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Atribua um array contendo <code>\"Luz\"</code> à variável <code>siblings</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" siblings = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Luz&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"];\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(siblings);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"17\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"23\" /><option startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"24\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"}\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"[ 'Luz' ]\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>[</code> seguido de <code>\"Luz\"</code> e finalmente <code>]</code>.</p></body></html>"
